column2: SELECT s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, ga.oiii_#_flux, ga.oiii_#_flux_err, (sph.modelmag_u-sph.modelmag_r), sph.modelmag_r-#*log1#(#E+#*sph.z)+# as M_r    INTO mydb.tremonti_all_filt  FROM GalSpecLine as ga, specobj as s, Galaxy as g, SpecPhoto as sph      WHERE s.class = &&&   AND s.specobjid = g.specobjid    AND s.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND sph.specobjid = g.specobjid   AND sph.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND ga.oiii_#_flux_err > #   AND g.specobjid > #   AND sph.z > #   AND (sph.modelmag_u-sph.modelmag_r) > #   AND M_r < #
